metadata.name: POWER OF NATURE
metadata.description:
I feel the power and strength of nature with every cell of my body. I feel the solid earth heated by the sun's rays. There is nothing unnecessary to prevent me from connecting with nature. The runes are ancient symbols that contain the power and wisdom of the ancestors. I can feel them on my skin...
Now follow me, follow my example. Get rid of the unnecessary and feel these vibrations...

(more in one of the additional files I'll send you)
